Message_0_Page_0 I might as well explain the origins of my arrival here, and why I remain. Before the outbreak, I was sent by the U.S. to spy on the strange events going on in this region. Now that the world is in ruin, my mission no longer requires any secrecy.
Message_0_Page_1 But I still believe that the events here are the cause of the original outbreak, for I have seen countless truly strange things in this Oblast. So much so, that my heart and mind need answers, and I have come here to find out what lies in the shielded chamber below us.
Message_0_Page_2 These are dire times, and we must rely on each and every man and woman, that still exists. I am willing to trade some things with you.